# .mailmap — display mapping for historical commits.
#
# Format: <canonical name> <canonical email> <old name> <old email>
#
# git tools (log, blame, shortlog) and GitHub honor this file to display
# historic commits under the maintainer's canonical identity without
# rewriting git history. SHAs stay stable, tags stay valid, forks stay
# in sync.

Tomasz Małozięć <225959895+tmaloziec@users.noreply.github.com> Tomek <tomek@build-on-ai.dev>
